{
  "stem": "4967.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "Lice used to come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "They come in your head, next to your private parts, and under the arms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "There we used to shave every week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "The Jewish barbers, it was special barbers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "My late uncle was a barber in the camp too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "And he used to shave whatever he had to shave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "There's no extra privileges.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "The only privilege was not to walk 10 kilometers a day to work outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "And two or three weeks later, they called up those children, the 130 or 135.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "They marched them to the railway station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "And as far as I know, they were cremated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "As far as I know, those days they were cremated in Dachau main camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 138,
      "text": "But after the war, I find out they were actually sent, transported by rail, to Poland back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 139,
      "text": "And there were very few survivors of them after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 140,
      "text": "They put up two poles a certain height.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 141,
      "text": "Any child who went through those two poles went to the gas chamber, to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 142,
      "text": "Who was bigger, taller survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 143,
      "text": "And they kept them in-- in the camp as the messenger boy, as the cleaner boy, as this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 144,
      "text": "But these smaller guys who went through this particular outfit, particular frame, went to their death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 145,
      "text": "And-- and the winter came on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 146,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 147,
      "text": "And there was a really big German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 148,
      "text": "I've forgotten his name, SS man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 149,
      "text": "And one day [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was a [INAUDIBLE] alarm, was a siren.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 150,
      "text": "Enemy planes overhead or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 151,
      "text": "So we went in to the trenches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 152,
      "text": "I counted myself 5,000 planes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 153,
      "text": "They were big as little flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 154,
      "text": "And one smaller plane used to make a smoke mark, a round circle in the sky.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 155,
      "text": "And they were flying very high.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
